      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To direct the Federal Trade Commission to conduct an investigation and submit to Congress a report on unfair or deceptive acts or practices that may be prevalent in the advertising or marketing of firearms and to issue regulations to prohibit unfair or deceptive acts or practices related to the advertising or marketing of firearms, and for other purposes.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
